<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="el">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Κλειδί Απαντήσεων — {{ title }}</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #111;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      max-width: 860px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Header ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .sheet-header {
      border-bottom: 3px solid #c62828;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .sheet-title {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #c62828;
    }
    .sheet-subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }
    .sheet-meta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 32px;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #444;
    }

    /* ── Warning banner ──────────────────────────────────────── */
    .key-warning {
      background: #fff3e0;
      border-left: 5px solid #ff9800;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
      color: #e65100;
    }

    /* ── Exercise grid ───────────────────────────────────────── */
    .exercises {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ columns }}, 1fr);
      gap: 14px 20px;
    }
    .exercise-cell {
      position: relative;
      border: 1.5px solid #ffcdd2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 18px 12px 14px 12px;
      min-height: 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: #fff8f8;
    }
    .exercise-num {
      position: absolute;
      top: 5px;
      left: 8px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
    .exercise-text {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .answer-part {
      color: #c62828;
    }

    /* ── Footer ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .sheet-footer {
      margin-top: 28px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .sheet-footer .id {
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #bbb;
      font-family: monospace;
    }

    /* ── Print ───────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .print-bar { margin-top: 28px; text-align: center; }
    .print-btn {
      background: #c62828; color: #fff; border: none;
      padding: 10px 28px; font-size: 15px; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer;
    }
    .print-btn:hover { background: #8b0000; }

    @page { size: A4; margin: 18mm 20mm; }
    @media print {
      .print-bar { display: none; }
      body { padding: 0; max-width: 100%; }
      .exercise-cell { break-inside: avoid; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="sheet-header">
    <div class="sheet-title">🔑 Κλειδί Απαντήσεων</div>
    <div class="sheet-subtitle">{{ title }}</div>
    <div class="sheet-meta">
      {% if child_name %}<span>Μαθητής: <strong>{{ child_name }}</strong></span>{% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="key-warning">
    ⚠️ Αυτό το φύλλο είναι για τον γονιό / δάσκαλο. Μην το δείξεις στο παιδί πριν λύσει τις ασκήσεις.
  </div>

  <div class="exercises">
    {% for ex in exercises %}
    <div class="exercise-cell">
      <span class="exercise-num">{{ loop.index }}.</span>
      {# Split answer_text at " = " to colour the answer part red #}
      {% set parts = ex.answer_text.rsplit(' = ', 1) %}
      <span class="exercise-text">
        {{ parts[0] }} = <span class="answer-part">{{ parts[1] }}</span>
      </span>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>

  <div class="sheet-footer">
    {% if micro_skill_meta %}
    <div style="font-size:12px; color:#888; margin-bottom:6px;">
      Δεξιότητα: {{ micro_skill_meta.name_el }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Επίπεδο {{ micro_skill_meta.difficulty_level }}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="id">ID: {{ instance_id }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="print-bar">
    <button class="print-btn" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Εκτύπωση Κλειδιού</button>
  </div>

</body>
</html>

